00:00:53.378 --> 00:01:05.205
 Using your Windows account with your Microsoft account, you can download apps from the App Store and sync your PC experience online. 

00:01:05.205 --> 00:01:12.561
 Type 'Windows + C' to run the Chamber and then click Settings. 

00:01:12.561 --> 00:01:18.209
 Click 'Change PC settings' and then click the user menu. 

00:01:18.209 --> 00:01:22.224
 Click the "Use Microsoft account" button. 

00:01:22.224 --> 00:01:27.112
 Enter your e-mail address and click the Next button. 

00:01:27.112 --> 00:01:35.151
 If you do not have a Microsoft account, you can create a Microsoft account by clicking 'Create a new email address'. 

00:01:35.151 --> 00:01:41.104
 Enter the correct password for your e-mail address and click the Next button. 

00:01:41.104 --> 00:01:45.477
 Click Finish when you're done changing your account. 

00:01:45.477 --> 00:01:52.703
 Type 'Windows + C' to run the Chamber and then click Power. 

00:01:52.703 --> 00:01:56.950
 Click 'Restart' to restart your system. 

00:01:56.950 --> 00:02:02.397
 You can now log in to your Microsoft account. 

00:02:07.986 --> 00:02:15.989
 If you lose your login password, you can change your connected Microsoft password and log in. 

00:02:15.989 --> 00:02:24.665
 Run Internet Explorer on a PC with Internet access and access the live.com website. 

00:02:24.665 --> 00:02:28.796
 Click 'Can not access your account?' 

00:02:28.796 --> 00:02:35.226
 Enter your Microsoft account and the characters shown in the picture, then click the Next button. 

00:02:35.226 --> 00:02:43.143
 In the Reset Password option, select the Reset link Receive by e-mail and click the Next button. 

00:02:43.143 --> 00:02:49.726
 The mail account for password verification will be sent a new set of passwords. 

00:02:49.726 --> 00:02:53.700
 Now, connect to your password verification mail account. 

00:02:53.700 --> 00:02:59.395
 Click 'Reset Microsoft account password' in your inbox. 

00:02:59.395 --> 00:03:07.941
 Click 'Internet address' just below 'If you have requested this password reset, please go to'. 

00:03:07.941 --> 00:03:12.205
 The page to reset the password for Internet Explorer opens. 

00:03:12.205 --> 00:03:18.094
 On the newly opened page, enter the password you want to change and click the Next button. 

00:03:18.094 --> 00:03:20.505
 Your password change is complete. 

00:03:20.505 --> 00:03:27.727
 Simply connect your PC with the lost password to the Internet and log in with the changed password. 

